summary:
Active and resourceful recent BCom graduate with exceptional communication and interpersonal skills. Ability to multitask as shown by maintaining multiple extracurricular activities and upholding competitive GPA. I highly value integrity, hard work, and a positive attitude! 

Relocating to the Netherlands - looking for work opportunities in market research, digital marketing, branding, or anything else that may pop up!
